    {
      "id": "cli-nb.tmx:tu17@tmx-cdd21575",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Create a new kapi project with a {name}.kapi recipe and an\nadjacent .kapi/ state directory.\n\nBy default the project id is the current directory's basename and\nsource/target locales are en / (none). Override with --name,\n--source-locale, --target-locale (repeatable).\n\n--framework <name> pre-fills the content mapping for a known stack's i18n\ncatalogs (see 'kapi presets list --framework'): react-i18next, react-intl,\nnextjs, vue-i18n, flutter, angular."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Opprett et nytt kapi-prosjekt med en {name}.kapi-oppskrift og en\ntilhørende .kapi/-tilstandskatalog.\n\nSom standard er prosjekt-id-en navnet på gjeldende katalog, og\nkilde-/målspråk er en / (ingen). Overstyr med --name,\n--source-locale, --target-locale (kan gjentas).\n\n--framework <name> forhåndsutfyller innholdskartleggingen for i18n-katalogene\ntil en kjent teknologistakk (se 'kapi presets list --framework'): react-i18next,\nreact-intl, nextjs, vue-i18n, flutter, angular."
          }
        ]
      },
      "origins": [
        {
          "source": "import",
          "key": "cli-nb.tmx",
          "addedAt": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
          "addedBy": "kapi tm import",
          "sessionId": "tmx-cdd215754c1e270a-1781164979013541594"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
